  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Feature request : ability to save snapshot (from `evm_snapshot`) to disk and allow to load them\r\nIt would also be good if we could associate them with the compiler cache too so we can load them only if there were no change to contracts \r\n\r\nThis will speed up running test that rely on evm_snapshot as these still need to execute deployment and this is the current bottleneck for my test, especially when I want to run just a few of them\r\n\r\nSo I guess this is 2 feature\r\n\r\n- ability to save `evm_snapshot` to disk and load it back\r\n- ability to get contract cache id so we can save it along the snapshot and load it only if cache id matches\r\n",
